data.description: Just minutes from the JW Marriott, TPC Pkwy and an abundance of shopping and dining experiences!   This 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home features a gorgeous entry, a large flex space that is being used as a 5th room, the privacy of no back neighbors while on a greenbelt and a generously sized entertaining space.   The sellers spared no expense with their upgrades - quartz countertops, gas stovetop, coffee nook, floor to ceiling windows to name a few.   This home is exactly what you have been searching for!
